{"tid":1856184,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"奇文分享：你和藍絲及韓粉的距離沒有這樣遠","createTime":"2020-02-01T13:18:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-01T13:59:01.000Z","uid":276028,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"71d0cd8d98d80f6e2a74e87dccd6baf8dee4efb4","tid":1856184,"uid":276028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T13:18:18.000Z","msg":"網上找到。也許，我們和藍屍的分別，只是人生旅途上，決定的差異，就決定了我們是藍屍還是黃絲。<br />\n<br />\n我們，和藍絲及韓粉的距離，真是有這樣遠嗎？還是在人生不自覺、一剎間的抉擇，就決定了我們的分歧？「一子錯，滿盤皆落索」。就以我為例，若果人生的抉擇稍一不慎，現在我可能就會日日看方向日報、大公文匯（香港的親中共報紙）、日日支持特區政府和中共，變成了愚蠢的藍絲。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.boyangu.com/2019/07/taiwan_2020_hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.boyangu.com%2F2019%2F07%2Ftaiwan_2020_hk%2F&d=ANzGKs6Ysw%2B%2BKy1wioRXt7tp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=abbcd6b8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.boyangu.com/2019/07/taiwan_2020_hk/</a>"},{"pid":"91dd6ca4cc7b657f91298ce5f522e050fd33fb02","tid":1856184,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T13:25:00.000Z","msg":"星塵回憶錄 - 香港(一)　<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1856139\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1856139</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d6d1e6888964beeb992ced73814eb93eeae63ee3","tid":1856184,"uid":276028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91dd6ca4cc7b657f91298ce5f522e050fd33fb02","tid":1856184,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T13:25:00.000Z","msg":"星塵回憶錄 - 香港(一)　<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1856139\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1856139</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T13:31:17.000Z","msg":"謝謝！可惜P牌like不了。"},{"pid":"bea7b58032b14d75d2a5eb344e6d1f935fe82bd0","tid":1856184,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T13:59:01.000Z","msg":"間間茶餐廳部部電視機都長開播住ＴＶＢ<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/